@startuml
title Login Sequence (happy + error flows)
actor User
participant Browser
participant Server
participant Auth

User -> Browser: Open /accounts/login/
Browser -> Server: GET /accounts/login/
Server -> Browser: render login form (LoginForm)

User -> Browser: Enter credentials and submit
Browser -> Server: POST /accounts/login/
Server -> Auth: authenticate(username, password)
alt credentials valid
	Auth -> Server: return User
	Server -> Server: login(user) (creates session)
	Server -> Browser: redirect to dashboard (302)
else invalid credentials
	Auth -> Server: return None
	Server -> Browser: render login form with errors
	Browser -> User: show error "Invalid username or password"
end

@enduml
